1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,160
First we demonstrate that tree is absent. apt update refreshes repository metadata, and apt install adds the package through the supported package manager instead of copying an unmanaged binary.

2
00:00:12,510 --> 00:00:24,670
dpkg-query verifies package state. We then create the exact one-line package report required by the lab, including a final newline.

3
00:00:25,020 --> 00:00:33,820
The pipeline extracts field four from every access-log row, sorts equal status codes together, counts adjacent values, and swaps the count and status into the requested order.

4
00:00:34,170 --> 00:00:50,890
The final cat command exposes both deliverables. In particular, the status report must contain 404 followed by 3 before the automated check can pass.
